# The Cantaloupe distribution contains documentation and optional native
# dependencies that are not part of the OLDAP image. Send only the runtime JAR
# and OLDAP-owned configuration to the Docker builder.
**
!Dockerfile
!cantaloupe-oldap/
!cantaloupe-oldap/cantaloupe.properties
!cantaloupe-oldap/delegates.rb
!cantaloupe-*/
!cantaloupe-*/cantaloupe-*.jar
